<p style="text-align: justify;" align="center"><span style="font-family: 'Abyssinica SIL';"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>Return Policy</strong></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 'Abyssinica SIL';"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000;">The House Goods has a &ldquo;no questions asked return and refund policy,&rdquo; which entitles all users who have purchased a product on the House Goods to return the product at the time of delivery if they are not satisfied with the quality of the product</span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 'Abyssinica SIL';"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000;">Return Policy: If you want to return a product, please keep the product in the original packaging. In addition, the product must be unused and unwashed, with all tags intact</span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 'Abyssinica SIL';"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000;">To pass feedback to the merchants to improve the services, it is mandatory to share the images of the items, which you were dissatisfied with. Subject to acceptance from the third-party seller of the product, the Company may take the returned product back and grant credit/coupon in lieu of the value of the returned product. Such credit shall be available for use against a subsequent invoice for transactions on the House Goods.</span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 'Abyssinica SIL';"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000;">You may request for a refund/replacement within 7 days of delivery, Grocery products with all original tags &amp; packaging intact in case of any quality issues. It is also requested that a user should check if the product seal is intact (i.e., not broken) while accepting the order to avoid any kind of damage-related complaints post delivery</span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 'Abyssinica SIL';"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000;">Please note: Few items listed may or may not carry a seller warranty to which House Goods will support a basic return policy</span></span></span></p>
